&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Concept Development &amp;amp; Scriptwriting: Translate high-level creative visions established by the Creative Manager into actionable execution plans, generating innovative story suggestions, outlines, and finalized scripts.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pre-Production Plan Strat

